  "translations": {
    "en": "angels of light to the mu’adhins. With them will be standards and banners of light. They will come forth on riding animals – their front will be of green aquamarine, and their sacks will be of strong musk. The mu’adhins will ride them, and they will stand on them as they are led by the angels. They will call the adhan at the top of their voice. Then, he wept heavily until I sobbed and wept. When he went quiet, I said: What are you crying about? He said: Woe to you – you reminded me of things. I heard my beloved and my elite one (s) say: “By He who raised me in truth as a prophet! They will pass by the creation, standing on their animals, saying: ‘Allah is the Greatest! Allah is the Greate",
